summary: Otp Doodle ft My OC's by krystalfan-2  Used this base here by mh-presents. I know it’s more meant for a tall and short couple,...
caption:
Otp Doodle ft My OC’s by krystalfan-2

Used this base here by mh-presents. I know it’s more meant for a tall and short couple, but I couldn’t help but pass this one up. I mean, normally Chris is the one picking Mozzart up seeing as he, ya know…actually works out and has loads of upper body strength. However, the idea of Mozzart trying to reciprocate is pretty funny. He needs to put his bf down though. He’s going to get a hernia or pass out from lack of oxygen.

summary: Commissions since school is starting up again next week!  This time I’m offering my newer coloring style as an option for...
caption:
Commissions since school is starting up again next week! 

This time I’m offering my newer coloring style as an option for commissions and it is also slightly cheaper (Since it’s faster for me to do in compassion to my other style)! 

When emailing me please tell me if you would like Color Style 1 or 2 ! I use Paypal invoice for payments and will require half of the payment once I finish sketching your commission. (Full payment is required for Sketch Commissions) 

Reblogs are appreciated! ♥ Feel free to DM me if you have any questions or would just like a quote on something :)

summary: Doing some random outfit august since the chances of catching up are nonexistent heh. This one’s day 17′s space.  Random...
caption:
Doing some random outfit august since the chances of catching up are nonexistent heh. This one’s day 17′s space. 

Random funfact, grew up in a more rural area [it was on the top of a small mountain and didn’t even have street lights] so light pollution was nonexistent which meant when the sun went down you had a very clear view of stars. Never really got into constellations but did learn both dippers and the North Star and used to be able to locate it quite easily. It’s been one of favorite constellations since.
